<?xml version='1.0' encoding="UTF-8"?>

<book xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" version="5.0" xml:lang="en">
    
    <bookinfo>
        <title>ESUI - Pager</title>
    </bookinfo> 
    
	<section>   
        <title>继承层级</title>
		<para>Pager - Control</para>
	</section>

    <section>   
        <title>说明</title>
        <para>Pager用于控制列表翻页的选择。Pager控件的起始页数从0开始。</para>
    </section>
    
    <section>   
        <title>构造器静态参数配置</title>
        <table frame="topbot" align="left">
            <title>构造器静态参数配置</title>
            <tgroup cols="2">
                <thead>
                    <row>
                        <entry>名称</entry>
                        <entry>描述</entry>
                    </row>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <row>
                        <entry>{number} SHOW_COUNT</entry>
                        <entry>当页数较多时，中间显示页码的个数。</entry>
                    </row>
                </tbody>
            </tgroup>
        </table>
    </section>
    
    <section>   
        <title>初始化参数</title>
        <table frame="topbot" align="left">
            <title>初始化参数</title>
            <tgroup cols="2">
                <thead>
                    <row>
                        <entry>名称</entry>
                        <entry>描述</entry>
                    </row>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
					<row>
                        <entry>{boolean} disabled</entry>
                        <entry>控件的不可用状态。</entry>
                    </row>
					<row>
                        <entry>{HTMLElement} main</entry>
                        <entry>控件主元素。</entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>{number} page</entry>
                        <entry>当前页码。</entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>{number} showCount</entry>
                        <entry>当页数较多时，中间显示页码的个数。</entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>{number} total</entry>
                        <entry>总页数。</entry>
                    </row>

                </tbody>
            </tgroup>
        </table>
    </section>
     
     <section>   
        <title>公共实例方法</title>
        <table frame="topbot" align="left">
            <title>公共实例方法</title>
            <tgroup cols="2">
                <thead>
                    <row>
                        <entry>名称</entry>
                        <entry>描述</entry>
                    </row>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
					<row>
                        <entry>{void} appendTo( {HTMLElement} wrap )</entry>
                        <entry>将控件添加到页面的某个元素中。</entry>
                    </row>
					<row>
                        <entry>{void} disable( {void} )</entry>
                        <entry>设置控件状态为禁用。</entry>
                    </row>
					<row>
                        <entry>{void} enable( {void} )</entry>
                        <entry>设置控件状态为启用。</entry>
                    </row>
					
                    <row>
                        <entry>{number} getPage( {void} )</entry>
                        <entry>获取当前页码。</entry>
                    </row>
					<row>
                        <entry>{boolean} isDisabled( {void} )</entry>
                        <entry>获取控件可用状态。</entry>
                    </row>
					<row>
                        <entry>{void} render( {void} )</entry>
                        <entry>绘制控件。</entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>{void} setPage( {number} page )</entry>
                        <entry>选择页码。</entry>
                    </row>
                </tbody>
            </tgroup>
        </table>
    </section>
    
    <section>   
        <title>事件</title>
        <table frame="topbot" align="left">
            <title>事件</title>
            <tgroup cols="2">
                <thead>
                    <row>
                        <entry>名称</entry>
                        <entry>描述</entry>
                    </row>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <row>
                        <entry>{boolean} onchange: ( {number} page )</entry>
                        <entry>当选择的页码发生改变时触发。</entry>
                    </row>
                </tbody>
            </tgroup>
        </table>
    </section>
</book>